          <div class="layer-head">
            <div class="layer-num">05 / APPLICATIONS &amp; AGENTS</div>
            <h3 class="layer-name">Sovereign AI, agents, skills.</h3>
            <p class="layer-desc">Domain agents, vertical apps, and MCP-style skills running on your infrastructure — citizen services, CBDC, defence copilots, finance assistants, healthcare AI.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="layer-visual">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 560 110" class="tech draw" aria-hidden="true">
